emotes.msg: I have put out a bounty on Wharu and the Atua ngamaru. I will reward anyone who brings me proof of their deaths.
I'll reward handsomely for Carenzi pelts, Siraluun claws, Drudge charms, and Golem hearts--but only the right kinds.

But...how could you have come by this pendant? No Aun would willingly give up his pendant, given to him at birth. You must have slain one of my brothers! Bukha!  Get away from me, before I call upon Audetaunga to smother you!
When you murdered one of my brothers you proved yourself to be an enemy of the Aun.  I shall not even speak to you.

Thank you!  I have always enjoyed making weapons from the claws of the fearsome Siraluun. Let me make you a weapon out of this claw.

If you happen upon another of these claws and you do not wish for a weapon, I suggest you visit Merlonna Farel in the town of Bluespire. When last I ventured into that town, she mentioned in passing that she knew of someone who was looking for these claws as well.
